I completed the **`fetch-historical-command`** task - creating an artisan command to backfill historical spot prices from the ENTSO-E API.

### Files Created:

1. **`laravel/app/Console/Commands/BackfillSpot.php`** - New command
   - Command signature: `spot:backfill --start-date= --end-date= --force`
   - Defaults to 1 year of historical data when no dates specified
   - Fetches prices in monthly chunks to avoid API limits
   - Shows progress bar during long operations
   - Skips periods with existing data (unless --force)
   - 150ms delay between API calls to respect rate limits
   - Continues processing after individual chunk failures
   - Uses correct VAT rates based on date (10%, 24%, or 25.5%)
